description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Power Rock Row' from the channel Aisyah Rafaee.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor rowing.
It's suitable for Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Rhythmic Powerhouse and The Warrior Workout vibe.
The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly. The The Warrior Workout vibe means Unleash your inner beast. Sweat-dripping, heart-pounding, primal energy. This is especially good for Days when you want to destroy stress and feel invincible..
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Turn up the volume and rock our with Aishyah and Mike in this power-focused session in Long Beach. 

Max rhythm: 32, Format:  Interval...
